        {
            "title": "中國股市險升0.01%，創業板指止步5連陽，盤中一度創近11年新高",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Nvib4xSMzsyQIvZwgu7Dkw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXNPEAAG092_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>Investing.com - </strong>周三，4月15日，A股市場高開低走，滬指驚險收升，深成指跌近1%，創業板指盤中一度逼近3600點，創近11年新高，隨後轉跌止步5連陽。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">今日市場跌多升少，全市場超1800只個股上升，超3500只下跌。滬深兩市成交額2.42萬億，較上一個交易日放量315億。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">截至收市，上證綜合指數收升0.01%，報4027.21點，深證成份指數收跌0.97%，報14498.45點，創業板綜合指數收跌1.22%，報3514.96點，中國A50期貨指數截稿前升0.01%，報15318點。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-bf5a9895-1c68-356d-baad-ea0233c7d6e6-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"580\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/5hVGZpLlx3Kk_Y9bgYWYaw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU4MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/investing_com_hk_986/383df0da8df07c17e5912bf9e294f53b\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">盤面上，醫藥板塊逆勢拉升，哈藥股份2連板，津藥藥業、博瑞醫藥、金陵藥業、鷺燕醫藥等10餘股升停。算力租賃概念反復走強，利通電子2連板，協創數據、宏景科技大升續創歷史新高。商業航太概念表現活躍，神劍股份升停創歷史新高，華菱線纜升停。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">下跌方面，鋰電池概念集體調整，海科新源跌超12%，孚日股份跌停，華盛鋰電跌超8%。算力硬件方向沖高回落，特發資訊、新易盛、仕佳光子紛紛下挫。存儲晶片概念走弱，大為股份觸及跌停。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">巨豐投顧郭一鳴指出，從當日市場表現看，A股已呈現明顯的分化與乏力信號。4月底業績披露視窗期臨近，「業績雷」風險集中釋放，將進一步壓制市場風險偏好。綜合來看，A股修復行情已進入尾聲階段，短期大概率開啟震盪調整，當然指數或許不會立刻進入調整趨勢，但反復重心回落概率大。</p><blockquote class=\"border-pebble mx-5 my-7.5 border-l-2 pl-5 italic\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-dolphin\"><strong> </strong></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-dolphin\"><strong><u><span>美股財報季來襲，</span></u></strong><strong><u><span>Warren AI</span></u></strong><strong><u><span>一鍵解讀數據！現在</span></u></strong><strong><u><span>InvestingPro</span></u></strong><strong><u><span>立享</span></u></strong><strong><u><span>50%</span></u></strong><strong><u><span>折扣，</span></u></strong> <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"即刻點擊訂閱\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:即刻點擊訂閱;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.investing.com/pro/pricing?utm_medium=feed&amp;utm_source=yahoo&amp;utm_campaign=yahoo-hk\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><strong><em><span>即刻點擊訂閱</span></em></strong></a><strong><u><span>！</span></u></strong></p><figure class=\"mb-modu